What We Did This Session
Today was the final lab session for the physical prototype. The main goals were to finish the Mernda router setup, get all three routers connected properly, configure VLANs on each switch, add firewall rules on the VM, and verify that all campuses could communicate. By the end of the session everything was working and tested.

