Firewall Rules on ACS VM
We added Windows Firewall rules on the CBD campus VM to replicate the ACL rules from our Packet Tracer design. All commands were run in an elevated Command Prompt using netsh advfirewall.
Three rules were added:

Block IoT (192.168.30.0/24) from reaching Clinical (192.168.20.0/24)
Block Guest (192.168.40.0/24) from reaching Clinical (192.168.20.0/24)
Block Guest (192.168.40.0/24) from reaching Admin (192.168.10.0/24)

